item.title: Dev Processs
item.description: Dev Process # To Do # In progress # Creating branch # git checkout main git checkout -b {issue type}-{issue number} Commit messages # #{issuenumber} concise, descriptive message If you need to include more information, put it in the issue itself or the pull request please do not put a detailed commit description, i.e. keep it under 50 characters Creating a PR (Pull Request) # Search our repository for open or closed Pull Requests that relate to your submission.
